flowchart TD
    A([User opens VulnForm]) --> B[Enter CVE ID]
    B --> C{prefilledCveId\nfrom Intelligence tab?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Auto-fill CVE ID field\nscroll form into view]
    D --> E[Trigger handleNvdLookup automatically]
    C -- No --> F[CVE ID onBlur]
    F --> G[findDuplicateCve against\nin-memory vulnerabilities]
    G --> H{Match found?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Show inline amber warning\nwith existing record details]
    H -- No --> J[No inline warning]

    B --> K[User clicks Look up button]
    K --> E
    E --> L[Promise.allSettled:\nlookupNvd + lookupEpss in parallel]

    L --> M{NVD result?}
    M -- not_found --> N[Show error: CVE not found]
    M -- rate_limited --> O[Show error: rate limit]
    M -- network_error --> P[Show error: unreachable]
    M -- malformed --> Q[Show error: unexpected response]
    M -- Success --> R[Auto-fill: title, cvssScore\nmark fields with blue highlight]

    L --> S{EPSS result?}
    S -- Error --> T[Silent: supplementary data\nEPSS fields stay empty]
    S -- Success --> U[Auto-fill: epssScore, epssPercentile\nmark fields with blue highlight]
    U --> V{epssScore >= 0.70 AND\nexploitability != Actively Exploited?}
    V -- Yes --> W[Show amber suggestion:\nconsider Actively Exploited]
    V -- No --> X

    R --> X[User completes remaining fields:\nassetCriticality · exploitability\ndaysSinceDiscovery · affectedAssetCount\ninternetFacing]
    W --> X
    T --> X

    X --> Y[User clicks Calculate & Add]
    Y --> Z[validate form fields]
    Z -- Validation errors --> AA[Display inline field errors\nhalt submission]
    Z -- Valid --> AB[findDuplicateCve on form.cveId]
    AB --> AC{Duplicate found?}
    AC -- Yes --> AD[setShowDuplicateModal = true]
    AD --> AE[DuplicateCveModal shown\nsee diagram 04 for branch logic]
    AE -- Cancel --> AF[Close modal, stay on form]
    AE -- Submit Anyway --> AG
    AE -- Reopen Existing --> AH[changeVulnerabilityStatus\nRisk Re-opened\nsee diagram 04]
    AC -- No --> AG[proceedWithSubmit\nscoreVulnerability with weights + thresholds]
    AG --> AI[createVulnerability → PocketBase\nstatus: Open]
    AI --> AJ[Write audit log: action=create]
    AJ --> AK[Prepend new record to state]
    AK --> AL[Background: syncKevFeed\nfor new record only]
    AL --> AM{New KEV match?}
    AM -- Yes --> AN[Re-fetch all vulns from PB\nupdate state + lastKevSync]
    AM -- No --> AO([Form reset, ready for next entry])
    AN --> AO
